  <description>D&amp;D classes for RimWorld. Rare Hero pawns bear a class central to their identity: levels 1 to 20, Vancian spell slots, death saving throws, a transforming class vestment with inlay slots, and a retinue of job-specialized mim followers. Heroes delve themed dungeons for loot and capstone weapons, backed by a growing fantasy bestiary.

Requires Mooloh's D&amp;D Menagerie. In active development and tuned through play, so feedback and bug reports are welcome.</description>
